These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
House: cottage, farmhouse, wooden, cape-cod, futuristic, ranch-style, townhouse
7 different pets are kept: fish, goat, cat, bird, guinea-pig, lizard, rabbit
 1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the cape-cod house##1
 3. the townhouse house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 5. the wooden house is in the middle##1
 6. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
 7. the futuristic house is the owner of the fish##1
 8. the cottage house is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 9. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
10. the owner of the bird is on the left of the wooden house##1
11. the townhouse house is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| House           | futuristic | cape-cod | farmhouse | wooden | cottage | ranch-style | townhouse |
| Pet   | fish    | guinea-pig   | bird      | lizard | cat    | goat    | rabbit         |

