.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: february, november, may, april, july, january, september
There are 7 different favourite colors: blood-red, brown, black, emerald, aquamarine, lilac, turquise
 1. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
 3. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 7. the person who likes aquamarine is in the middle##1
 8. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Birthday          | february | november | july | april | january | september | may |
| Color   | brown      | black   | emerald   | aquamarine      | blood-red       | turquise       | lilac     |

