.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: amber, emerald, lilac, mauve, grey, fuchsia, purple
City: nizza, hannover, san-francisco, paris, colone, liverpool, edinburgh
 1. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
 4. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 5. the person traveling to nizza is the person who likes grey##1
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 7. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
 9. the person who likes fuchsia is the person traveling to paris##1
10. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
11. the person traveling to paris is in the middle##1
12. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Color   | emerald | grey     | lilac  | fuchsia       | amber       | purple  | mauve   |
| City    | liverpool  | nizza | edinburgh | paris | hannover | san-francisco | colone |

