.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
7 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rabbit, goat, turtle, dog, ferret, hedgehog
The people have 7 different jobs:  scientist, bartender, teacher, security-guard, firefighter, musician, freelancer
 1. the owner of the dog is the bartender##1
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the musician is on the right of the teacher##1
 4. the scientist is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
 7. the teacher is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the right of the musician##1
 9. the owner of the goat is the firefighter##1
10. the firefighter is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
11. the freelancer is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Pet   | ferret    | hedgehog     | turtle     | goat      | rabbit | dog      | guinea-pig     |
| Job   | security-guard | teacher | musician | firefighter | freelancer | bartender | scientist |

