 6. the person playing poker is on the right of the doctor##1
 7. the engineer is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 9. the person playing canasta is on the right of the mechanic##1
10. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
